author: ts:ez.no
msg: - Added ezcWebdavDigestAuthenticatorBase class, that might be extended by users
to not implement digest calculation on their own.
- Make PROPFIND requests return a global 403 if the requested resource itself
# If subsequent resources affected by the request are not accessible, 401 still
# appears in the Multistatus. We handle other request like this and cadaver
# acts most reasonable in this combination.
